.TH man 7 "27 Set 2015" "1.0" "rltools man page"
.SH NAME
.B rltools
\- regular language tools
.SH SYNOPSIS
.BR rltools " \fIOPTION\fP... \fIFILE\fP..."
.SH DESCRIPTION
rltools is a package of resources used to manage and generate type-3 
formal language representations (finite automata, regular grammars and
regular expressions).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \--dfa\  file
Converts a nondeterministic finite automaton, either with or without
epsilon-moves, to a determinized finite automaton.
.TP
.BI \--gta\  file
Converts a regular grammar to a determinized finite automaton.
.TP
.BI \--atg\  file
Converts a determinized finite automaton to a regular grammar.
.TP
.BI \--rta\  file
Convers a regular expression to a determinized finite automaton.
.TP
.BI \--atr\  file
Converts a determinized finite automaton to a regular expression.
.SH AUTHOR
Written by Gustavo Zambonin and Matheus Ben-Hur de Melo Leite.
